},
"footnotes":[
[
"AMS = altered mental status; CNS = central nervous system; CSE = convulsive status epilepticus; ECMO = extracorporeal membrane oxygenation; EEG = electroencephalography."
],
[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"sup",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
"a"
]
},
"If CSE is suspected, treatment should begin before EEG is performed or results are available; if nonconvulsive status epilepticus is suspected, treatment most often should await EEG results."
]
]
